resources.string: All entries and a location of each on the GooglePlay Map.

A collection of information about how you use your money is important, thats why i built Nusu.Financial awareness is as important as keeping up with the stock markert, or something like being updated about anything specific, at a business scale, not having this information can be catastrophic at a cosmic level. Nusu provides a simple list of items of how you spend and how you earn because even the smallest detail matters when it comes to aweraness.
